### Step 3: Logo Handling

**Option A** (If no images available):
```typescript
const logoGradients = [
  'linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%)',
  'linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%)',
  'linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%)',
  'linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b 0%, #38f9d7 100%)',
];

// Assign based on executor ID hash
const gradient = logoGradients[executor.id.charCodeAt(0) % logoGradients.length];
```

**Option B** (If images exist in `public/executors/`):
```typescript
<img src={`/executors/${executor.slug}.png`} alt={executor.name} />
```

